---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About The HalfCourt"
	description="What this is and who's writing it."
	pubDate={new Date('July 01 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p>
		The HalfCourt is a basketball blog and newsletter. Film breakdowns, box-score
		deep dives, trade reactions, and the occasional bad take defended too
		confidently. If you watch the League closely and like arguing about it, you're
		in the right place.
	</p>

	<p>
		Posts run through the season on the <a href="/blog">blog</a>, and the best of
		it lands in the newsletter. No hot-take churn for its own sake — just honest
		analysis from someone who watches too much basketball.
	</p>

	<p>
		Want to reach out, pitch a topic, or tell me I'm wrong about your team?
		Find The HalfCourt on X, or reply to any newsletter email.
	</p>
</Layout>
